            <div class="bg-[#111827] p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">What is Open Source?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">August 15, 2024</p>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">Open source software (OSS) is software with publicly accessible source code that anyone can inspect, modify, and enhance.</p>
