                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Benefits of Open Source</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">August 18, 2024</p>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Transparency and security</li>
                    <li>Community collaboration</li>
                    <li>Cost-effectiveness</li>
                    <li>Faster innovation</li>
                </ul>
